  <description type="morphology">Stems and petioles glabrous or sparsely pilose, not viscid. Flowers: sepals 10-20
        mm, 0.7-1.1 times as long as spurs; petal blades 0-3 mm. 2n = 14.</description>
  <description type="phenology">Flowering spring-summer (Apr-Aug)</description>
